Pehle us folder me chalo jisme app.js file hai. Tumhare case me ye folder hai:

chapter7-npn and tools


uske liye terminal me type karo:

cd "chapter7-npn and tools"


âš¡ Important: Folder name me space hai isliye double quotes (" ") lagana zaroori hai.

Ab us folder ke andar ho jaoge.
Check karne ke liye:

dir


Isme tumhe app.js dikhna chahiye.

Ab file run karo Node.js se:

node app.js


